        "des": "<p>Can't find floor mats for your unique car? <br\/><br\/>We have contacts all over Poland and abroad with various car dealerships where we take measurements when you are unable to come to us. We approach each measurement with the perfection with which a watchmaker assembles a watch.<br\/><br\/>Fill out this form and we will realize individually tailored floor mats for your car.<\/p>",
